            <div id="projectpara">
                <h5>I had always loved the theme of futuristic and Cyber-punk. On top of my great interest and love in Anime and storylines, I want my escape room to be a unique and entertaining for all players. My VR game which is called: “ X-Chrono Edge-runner” is a futuristic sci-fi thrilling themed escape room that involves the element of Cyberpunk and Immersive Thrill that requires quick decision-making in order to get out alive. [You have been captured and placed in a top-secret cyber laboratory, but the twist is that a Time-Controlling device that had been activated by the scientists malfunctioned and the count down to the time stop can’t be stopped! Leaving you behind, the scientists activated the Room lockdown which seal the time effect of the machine just within that room and escaped, leaving you only a limited amount of time to escape before the TIME within the room got stopped! Either Escape alive or be frozen in time for eternity, will be up to your skills and speed!] This is a simple but unique plot behind the Escape room I had came up with, the name inspired by 2077 CyberPunk Edgerunner Anime , and the idea of time coming from the cyber-part within the Anime and Cyberpunk Game that accelerate time around you and attack before the enemies could react, but I made it a complete different new idea and concept that can be applied in an Escape room. Thank you for trying out the game!</h5>
