            <div id="projectpara">
                <h5>The Unique Selling Points of my VR game “X-Chrono Edge-runner” is that within the Laboratory, there are multiple layers of rooms and vaults which all the safe doors and entrances are locked down. Each Room are considered a “level” and the way to get out of them are each different and unique that will require a player to use his/her brain and act fast to find the key or code to opening and unlocking each entrance. Some rooms entrance might even require more than one “key” that can be found or created in the room itself! One cannot rely on a pattern or trend of previous rooms to solve and unlock the following as every one of them have a vastly different way to unlock! Each will also be more difficult than the previous. Therefore, beside using your brain, teaming up with another player (max 2) will greatly increase the chance and your speed of escaping the room! If you want to test your limits, try to escape all by yourself! If not, learn the importance of teamwork and coordination among others to escape together!</h5>
            </div>
